caseTags.name: tags/PFI-I-001605
caseTags.title: Admin console > G Suite Setup > Doesn't know [How to] setup MX Records (needs help with configuration, incorrectly sets up MX, unaware of 24hr propagation, MX reset after domain host change, etc.)
caseTags.description: Unaware of how to setup and validate MX records or sets up MX incorrectly, unaware of the 24 hr propagation, MX records may be reset of flushed or need to be set up again, name server issues, how to minimize mail flow disruption, invalid MX , etc

caseTags.name: tags/PFI-I-001599
caseTags.title: Admin console > G Suite Setup > Doesn't know [How to] Verify Domain (doesn't understand DNS, propagation delays, doesn't know how to access domain host or does not own domain, etc)
caseTags.description: Should be used irrespective of primary or secondary domain verification when the customer specifically needs support in the verification process.

caseTags.name: tags/PFI-I-003061
caseTags.title: Unsupported Products > Non-Google Products > [Unsupported Products] Non-Google Products
caseTags.description: This tag should be used for issues related to any Non-Google product as Outlook (when migrating away from GSuite), Skype, Facebook, etc. Use [Product] Unsupported instead if issue is about a non-Google product but impacts functioning of G Suite product.
